{
  "texts": [
    "Oracle Cerner has also integrated generative AI into its EHR.",
    "Recently, (Nov 2023), Oracle Cerner announced the Oracle Clinical Digital Assistant tool, a multimodal voice and screen-based tool that will participate in appointments by automating notetaking and proposing actions such as medication orders, labs, and followup appointments.",
    "Providers should be able to talk to the tool to access elements of a patient's EHR, while patients should be able to talk to the tool to book appointments and ask questions 12.",
    "In deciding to implement either Epic or Oracle Cerner's generative AI applications, Wornow et al. 's evaluation framework becomes important to assess each model's true clinical value.",
    "Below is a checklist to be used while conducting a model evaluation, stemming from Wornow et al. 's six points."
  ]
}